#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:60
msgid ""
"Fournir des solutions énergétiques durables et accessibles qui contribuent "
"au\n"
"                développement économique et social de la République "
"Démocratique du Congo."
msgstr ""
"To provide sustainable and accessible energy solutions thatcontribute to the "
"economic and social development of the DemocraticRepublic of the Congo."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:66
msgid ""
"Répondre aux besoins fondamentaux de la population en garantissant un accès "
"fiable,\n"
"                  sécurisé et durable à l’énergie électrique."
msgstr ""
"To meet the population's fundamental needs by guaranteeing reliable,secure "
"and sustainable access to electricity."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:71
msgid ""
"Contribuer de manière responsable au développement économique, social et\n"
"                  environnemental de la République Démocratique du Congo."
msgstr ""
"To contribute responsibly to the economic, social and "
"environmentaldevelopment of the Democratic Republic of the Congo."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:76
msgid ""
"Aller au-delà du rôle d’énergéticien en accompagnant et en sensibilisant "
"les\n"
"                  consommateurs à une utilisation responsable de "
"l’électricité, afin de renforcer leur satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"To go beyond the role of energy provider by supporting and raisingconsumer "
"awareness of responsible electricity use to strengthen theirsatisfaction."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:90
msgid "Notre Vision"
msgstr "Our Vision"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:92
msgid ""
"Être une référence nationale et un acteur central de la relance énergétique "
"durable en\n"
"                République Démocratique du Congo"
msgstr ""
"To be a national reference and a central player in sustainable "
"energyrecovery in the Democratic Republic of the Congo"

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:98
msgid ""
"Électrifier les zones rurales et urbaines afin de réduire les inégalités "
"d’accès à\n"
"                  l’électricité."
msgstr ""
"To electrify rural and urban areas in order to reduce inequalities inaccess "
"to electricity."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:103
msgid ""
"Promouvoir les énergies renouvelables et l’innovation pour des solutions "
"modernes et\n"
"                  durables."
msgstr ""
"To promote renewable energy and innovation for modern, sustainablesolutions."

#: twiga_power/templates/app/about.html:108
msgid ""
"Former la main-d’œuvre locale afin de renforcer les compétences et garantir "
"un service\n"
"                  de qualité."
msgstr ""
"To train the local workforce to strengthen skills and ensure qualityservice."

